  "description": "<p>🎊 <strong>FRESH SALES TALENT | Work with friends, ORD, Fresh grad, Career switch</strong> 🎊<br /></p><p>Hungry for success? Love talking to people? Want unlimited earning potential? <br />We’re looking for confident, driven individuals who enjoy closing deals and hitting targets💰<br /></p><p>🔥What You’ll Be Doing <br />- Actively engage customers and understand their needs<br />- Present and recommend suitable solutions clearly and confident<br />- Build dtrong customer relationships and follow up for conversions<br />- Work with your team to smash sales targets together 🎯<br /><br />💼 What We’re Looking For <br />- Positive, outgoing and goal-oriented attitude <br />- Comfortable talking to people and handling objections <br />- Sales-driven mindset with the hunger to earn more <br />- Fresh grads / career switch / ORD welcome <br /></p><p>💎 What You’ll Get <br />- 💰 Attractive commisions & incentives <br />- 🎓 1-to-1 mentorship & full sales training <br />- 📈 Clear career progression opportunities <br />- 🫂 Fun, energetic and supportive team culture <br />- ☄️ Weekly payouts <br />- ✈️ Travel Opportunities <br /></p><p><em><strong>APPLY NOW TO JOIN THE TEAM AND GROW TOGETHER!!</strong></em></p>",
